originalText.text:
Dr.Orenshein has been my dentist for 2 decades. From the first appointment I had till the present day,  Dr.Orenshein has repaired and improved my dental work beyond my expectations. Each and every time I had a problem without question he found a solution.
His demeanor is comforting with explaining each procedure and
professional expertise. I am in the entertainment industry.

paramount to my livelihood. I sincerely encourage  anyone looking for a 5 STAR dentist to visit Dr. Orenshein! I promise
you your smile will GLOW !!!

originalText.text: I've been seeing Orenshein for several years, after a recommendation from friends who have been seeing Orenshein since high school. The staff is wonderful, visits are quick and easy, and the dentist is no nonsense and doesn't try to upsell you on having unnecessary and/or cosmetic procedures. I broke a tooth last year and I needed a crown made quickly--Orenshein did it the same day! I really appreciated Orenshein's Covid-19 precautions, too.

The receptionist Natalie was condescending and didn’t really wanna help me. I also witnessed this Natalie woman arguing with the dentist about a person who was not able to make his appointment due to his child being sick and she wanted to charge him. The doctor was OK with letting it go but she was absolutely not, and she got her way, it was horrible witnessing what a cold heart this woman has. I would not go to this establishment you just gonna feel very uncomfortable.  I also had a problem with my bill and I wanted to repair and make arrangements but she was so nasty I mean I I don’t wanna deal with this woman at all and this establishment
it is only my opinion, but I do not recommend this establishment at all.

originalText.text: Dr. Orenshein was recommended me by a friend as an honest and highly professional dentist. More than ten year ago, he fixed all my dental issues without overcharging and any undesirable consequences. I highly recommend Dr. Orenshein to all those who are seeking professional and fair treatment.
